12.short_description: EMcube helps develop 3D coils of different properties by enabling creation of personal designs of different plastic combinations.

18.description:
At this moment 3D printers are becoming cheaper. However, the necessary supplies are still expensive (US$36/kg) and its price doesn't match with the real value (US$5/kg). EMcube is able to make user's personal 3D material from other 3D printings, plastic objects such as bottles, plastic bags, and other plastic-made objects in bulk. We aim to help people developing new 3D coils with different properties by enabling to create personal designs of different plastic combinations . This will increase the posibility of customizing and creating new materials. 
Our product is a simple machine which takes a wide range of small pieces of plastic as its printing supply, and extrudes it in order to make plastic coil. It can be used with any generic 3D printer. It's designed to be a modular product; therefore, users can add new modules either obtained from us or personally developed. We support any module modification made by users than significate an upgrade to the machine.
